Package model

Class CountryReportItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.CountryReportItem
  • public class CountryReportItem
extends java.lang.Object
    Class is a model for a row in the table generated by the Customers by Country report. Data members map to columns in the table. Includes data member getter and setter methods.

    See Also:
    CustomersByCountryReport
